Since I got some crazy threats in my messages from a girl, and uploaded a screenshot for everyone to report, Instagram have flagged my account 

Please go to settings, help, then Report A Problem.
Write my username and say that @fightthroughmentalhealth is not showing up in any hashtags and cannot ultilize their platform and promotions for their business.

Please send me a screenshot when done so I can personally thank you.💗 can’t do this without you guys!

Here are some ways to make someone who is suicidal feel loved:
• Listen to them, without judgement.
• Ask them if there is anything you can do to help.
• Be present.
• Remind them they are loved. 
💗💗💗💗💗
